\n有期徒刑、拘役或新臺幣一萬元以下罰金。","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/CHDM/109%2c%e8%a8%b4%2c983%2c20210505%2c3/pdf"},"JID":"CHDM,109,訴,983,20210505,3","JYEAR":"109","JCASE":"訴","JNO":"983","JDATE":"20210505","JTITLE":"違反藥事法"}